{"tid":1285328,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請理解身邊的人 適當地給予援手","createTime":"2019-07-04T13:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:42:35.000Z","uid":68668,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f71ebff109cbbd9c3d51471bc949f8526c048593","tid":1285328,"uid":68668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"「自殺往往是一種為了脫離苦海，卻找不到其他出路，在絕望之中以及衝動之下的行為。如果有其他方式可以不再痛苦，大部分的人不會選擇自殺。有時候，想要自殺的人，需要的不是別人告訴他怎麼做，而是多一些理解。理解不是認同，而是讓他有被了解、不孤單的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/104943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F104943&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRaCfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=032d1bda\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/104943</a><br />\n<br />\n只要肯適當地伸出援手<br />\n嘗試理解對方的想法<br />\n困難面前從不孤單<br />\n被理解的前題下人係會願意打開心門的<br />\n突然被衝破的念頭就會得到舒緩<br />\n<br />\n自殺行為係多重壓力被壓抑而突然爆發的結果<br />\n係社會係家庭壓力日積月累的問題造成<br />\n<br />\n再講多次<br />\n適當地伸出援手可以適切疏導負面情緒<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"e173bec0c18b43bbc8dd1295b47c8403afaef8b8","tid":1285328,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"幫手俾意見啦<br />\n<br />\n一人一信  no DQ  還我選舉權  <br />\n唔好比藉口人地將好的議員篩走<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F271467.typeform.com%2Fto%2FMTUjKV&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRaCfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=9fd9bc89\" target=\"_blank\">https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV</a>"},{"pid":"d4e1d8cce63bdcf745477189c285e53d44206925","tid":1285328,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset